{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"weekNumberingYear"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int"},{"kind":"text","text":" { "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"get"},{"text":" }","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This function, taken together with ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_date_time_get_week_of_year()"},{"text":" and","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_date_time_get_day_of_week()"},{"text":" can be used to determine the full ISO","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"week date on which "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"datetime"},{"text":" falls.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This is usually equal to the normal Gregorian year (as returned by"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_date_time_get_year()"},{"text":"), except as detailed below:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For Thursday, the week-numbering year is always equal to the usual"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"calendar year.  For other days, the number is such that every day"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"within a complete week (Monday to Sunday) is contained within the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"same week-numbering year."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"For Monday, Tuesday and Wednesday occurring near the end of the year,","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"this may mean that the week-numbering year is one greater than the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"calendar year (so that these days have the same week-numbering year"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"as the Thursday occurring early in the next year).","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"For Friday, Saturday and Sunday occurring near the start of the year,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"this may mean that the week-numbering year is one less than the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"calendar year (so that these days have the same week-numbering year","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"as the Thursday occurring late in the previous year).","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An equivalent description is that the week-numbering year is equal to"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the calendar year containing the majority of the days in the current","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"week (Monday to Sunday)."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note that January 1 0001 in the proleptic Gregorian calendar is a"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Monday, so this function never returns 0."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/DateTime\/weekNumberingYear","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"metadata":{"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"property","roleHeading":"Instance Property","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"weekNumberingYear","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"externalID":"s:4GLib16DateTimeProtocolPAAE17weekNumberingYearSivp::SYNTHESIZED::s:4GLib8DateTimeC","extendedModule":"GLib","modules":[{"name":"GLib"}],"title":"weekNumberingYear"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns the ISO 8601 week-numbering year in which the week containing"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"datetime","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" falls."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib","doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/DateTime","doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/DateTime\/DateTimeProtocol-Implementations"]]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/glib\/datetime\/weeknumberingyear"]}],"references":{"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib","title":"GLib","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/glib","abstract":[]},"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib/DateTime":{"title":"DateTime","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"DateTime"}],"abstract":[{"code":"GDateTime","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is a structure that combines a Gregorian date and time"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"into a single structure."}],"kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"DateTime","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/glib\/datetime","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/DateTime","type":"topic","role":"symbol"},"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib/DateTime/DateTimeProtocol-Implementations":{"role":"collectionGroup","kind":"article","title":"DateTimeProtocol Implementations","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/glib\/datetime\/datetimeprotocol-implementations","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/DateTime\/DateTimeProtocol-Implementations"},"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib/DateTime/weekNumberingYear":{"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Returns the ISO 8601 week-numbering year in which the week containing","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"datetime","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" falls."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"weekNumberingYear","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/DateTime\/weekNumberingYear","url":"\/documentation\/glib\/datetime\/weeknumberingyear","title":"weekNumberingYear"}}}